These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
City: new-york, colone, edinburgh, paris
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| City      | paris  | new-york | colone  | edinburgh |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, old-henry, ritmeester
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the game-smoker is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | old-henry | game   | bluemaster |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk, coffee
1. the person eating corn is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | coffee   | soy-milk | lemonade    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, trike, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the motorbike##2
4. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Transport   | taxi   | trike     | motorbike    | car       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, funk, folk, indie
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | indie | jazz | folk |

