.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, punk, metal
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5
3. the fan of metal is between the police-officer and the fan of punk##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Music-Genre   | punk        | metal     | ambient       | pop   |

