.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, time-travel, crime, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | documentary  | crime  | fantasy   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

