.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
4 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, rabbit, ferret
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Pet    | ferret | guinea-pig  | rabbit | rat |

