.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, milk
House: cottage, craftsman, wooden, ranch-style
1. the wooden house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
5. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
6. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| House       | cottage       | wooden   | ranch-style | craftsman |

