.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, folk, disco
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
2. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
5. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Music-Genre      | classical  | disco | funk | folk |

