.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, lilac, coral, blood-red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | mauve | lilac   | coral | blood-red     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

