.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, fish, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the owner of the fish##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| Pet         | fish  | turtle | goldfish | ferret |

