.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, salsa, blues, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, canadian, mexican
1. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the fan of blues##1
5. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | techno | salsa | blues |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

