.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bus, van, airplane
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, manager, mechanic
1. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the van and the person driving the bus##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Transport   | car | van  | airplane      | bus |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

