2. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
3. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Flower   | zinnia | marigold  | daisy | rose        |

